body:
Version 2.1.0

Framework:

- [Fix] BUG-10085 Do not expand factory ROM presets tree node by default
- [Fix] BUG-10084 Linux: Plugin editor cannot be operated after releasing
        the mouse

JE8086:

- [Sad] Removed the volume knob animation that "emulated" the loose knob
        from the hardware. Apparently most people never owned the hardware
        and thought it was a bug

NodalRed2x:

- [Imp] Added "secret" Notch filter type

OsTIrus:

- [Fix] Automation became incompatible with 2.0.15 due to Chorus Type parameter
        fix. Parameter versioning has been introduced to prevent this in the
        future. Parameters are now compatible with 2.0.14 and below again.
- [Fix] Fix Serial 6 routing displaying two times "4 Pole" instead of
        "4 Pole" and "2 Pole"
- [Fix] Typo "DESTENATION" on LFO page
- [Fix] Typo "CUTTOFF" on Filter page
- [Fix] Analogue filter modes button not lit if analogue modes page selected
